' Gambas class file

''' This class represents the visible part of a model as a label within a flow.
''' In BPMN this is the class **Label**.

Export
Inherits DiagramElement

' ###############################################
' BEGIN Element label functionality
' ###############################################

' -----------------------------------------------
' BEGIN Declarations, construction an destruction
' -----------------------------------------------

'' Gets the bounding box of this label. Override base class property.
Property Read Bounds As RectF

'' Store the bounds.
Private $oBounds As RectF = New RectF(0, 0, 0, 0)

' -----------------------------------------------
' END Declarations, construction an destruction
' -----------------------------------------------

' -----------------------------------------------
' BEGIN Properties implementation
' -----------------------------------------------

'' Private - no description.
Private Function Bounds_Read() As RectF
  Return $oBounds
End

' -----------------------------------------------
' END Properties implementation
' -----------------------------------------------

' -----------------------------------------------
' BEGIN Method implementation
' -----------------------------------------------

'' Sets bounding box of this label.
'' This method is hidden in the hope, that only deived and **friend** classes know and use this method.
''
'' The **boundsValue** defines the new bounding box of this label.
Public Sub _SetBounds(boundsValue As RectF)
  $oBounds = boundsValue
End

' -----------------------------------------------
' END Method implementation
' -----------------------------------------------

